Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:32.48,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:34.48,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,我懂得
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:36.36,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,只能上了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.36,0:01:37.45,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,只能上了
